0.3.0 (May 17, 2012)

	Added support to launch custom scripts by pressing the function button
	at the front of the unit. See README in further info.

	Changed licensing to MIT license.
	
	Fixed HDD temperature monitoring (thanks to user ewano)

        USB launch script /etc/init.d/usb needs BASH rather than DASH.

0.2.0 (June 5, 2010)

	Introduced support for fan speed regulation on
	system temperature, taken from hard disk S.M.A.R.T. information.

0.1.0 (May 14, 2010)

	Initial release, supporting:
	- system shutdown via back switch
	- power led control
	- USB power on/off
